Package: piledownR
Title: Per-Base Coverage from RNASeq BAMs
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("piledown authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: Computes per-base coverage (pileup) from RNASeq BAM files,
    tracking matched and skipped bases separately. Strand-aware using
    library fragment type (ISR/ISF). Returns Arrow RecordBatches.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports: arrow, nanoarrow
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.1
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
